data.description: Miami South Beach meets Pointe West in this rarely available villa with 2.5 car garage w 3rd bay for your golf cart. This home was built in 2005, then completely remodeled in 2023 with style!  Modern chic design touches are an attention getter in every detail including all new plank tile flooring throughout, new custom kitchen and luxury bathrooms w glass barn doors, stylish LED fixtures and fans, 2017 A/C installed in 2019, 2017 water heater, 2022 roof, functional Bahama shutters & more.  Just steps from the clubhouse, community pools, championship 18 hole golf course w driving range & more!
